"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-27-timetable-olympics-2024-schedule-day-1-21308425\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"TheParisOlympics are underway after aspectacular and historic opening ceremony got the Games off the groundin the French capital last night.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 114, \"end\": 120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.5272592933637985, \"rank\": 0.6863449833743793, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The stage is set for what promises to be a compelling fortnight of pulsating action and drama, withhigh hopes for Team GBacross 26 of the 32 sports on show across the Channel.\", \"from\": 142, \"to\": 317, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some of the competition already kicked off in the week - including football, rugby sevens and shooting - but today marks the official day one of the Games and there is so much to look forward to over the coming hours.\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for latest updates on the Paris Olympics  From a British perspective, Michael Bargeron and Seonaid McIntosh will aim to get their hands on Team GB's first medals of thesummerwhen the mixed air rifle finals get underway this morning.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 618, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.9804499054183442, \"rank\": 0.01975162201293007, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 660, \"end\": 676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seonaid_McIntosh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seonaid McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q1908